Alagarn <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uoctella.showPublicProfile?language=EN>octella</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/25/01 4:57:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13570.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re</span><hr size=1> well it is true a war will riposte more dodge more etc.<br>
but only a very small amount. think how many hits are riposted, then add a small percentage to that. it doesn't add up to much.<br>
<br>
