<br>
if you're saying both are in a group and who should tank. it doesn't matter, both will still be doing their melee damage. and i'm going to be stunning so the mob is not moving much.<br>
<br>
if you're trying to choose 1 over the other. well fully buffed i hit just at 5khp (well 4746 i think today in seb so sue me) and 1304-1326 ac. with that much ac wars and paladins are hitting the ac cap for mobs in seb/chardok/velks etc. meaning when hit we take about the same damage. however i'm stunning so much i'm rarely hit. while your war just swings and taunts and takes a beating.<br>
<br>
